From d2c322bd8cbd4cd86c631eaaf601464716dcca4e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Denisse Martinez <denisse@nearshorenavigator.com>
Date: Sat, 21 Mar 2026 07:45:31 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] fix(seo): eliminate duplicate FAQPage schema + add GA4
 reporting script
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Remove hardcoded generic FAQPage from city/service page.tsx — GSC was
  flagging "Duplicate field FAQPage" rich-result errors; ServiceLocationClient
  now owns the only authoritative FAQ schema per page
- Gate homepage FAQPage in SchemaMarkup.tsx behind usePathname() so it only
  emits on / and /[lang] routes, never on city/service pages
- AI Consultant, HeroScanner, AIChat, Questionnaire: Gemini 2.0 Flash upgrade
  and agent improvements
- Add llms.txt endpoint for LLM crawlers
- i18n: complete en/es locale coverage for questionnaire + new keys
- market_pulse_agent: Gemini-powered competitive intelligence
- scripts/ga4-report.mjs: GA4 Data API reporting script (analytics without
  opening browser; uses gcloud ADC — see script header for setup)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
